          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            To book an appointment, go to the "Book" section in the sidebar and fill out the booking form.
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-item">
          <div class="faq-question">
            â° What are your support hours and response times?
            <i class="fas fa-chevron-down"></i>
          </div>
          <div class="faq-answer">
            Our team is available <strong>Mondayâ€“Friday, 8:00 AM to 5:00 PM</strong>.  
            We typically respond within 24 hours.
          </div>
